channel.title: Webclient problem
channel.description:
Hey guys,
I have been working on making my webclient today. I did all the steps, jarred/signed it and all that shit. Then made an HTML file to run the actual webclient. When I run the html file from my computer the webclient loads fine in my browser.
So I then uploaded all my files to my web host including the cache and shit. But when I go to the actual webclient on the webpage it starts loading and then stays at a white screen.
Heres the link to my webclient: http://www.vintagepk.net/play.html (If that's considered advertising I'm sorry)
Anyone know what could be causing this problem?
